09:15.010 --> 09:15.730
Sudah tentu boleh.

09:15.970 --> 09:16.610
Sila duduk.

09:17.580 --> 09:18.650
Sila duduk di sini.

09:24.580 --> 09:25.540
Peguam sekalian,

09:26.130 --> 09:27.540
